      <description>
        
        
        &lt;figure&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;images/How-to-check-Bandwidth-consumption-in-Microhost-panel_utho.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;How to check Bandwidth consumption in Microhost panel&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
