&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Step 3. When you click on “Manage cloud” option , A window will appear shown in the image below. You need to select the “Analysis” option (By default its already on Analysis) . You can examine your CPU, Memory ,read/write ,traffic and Bandwidth utilization of the server with the help of graph .&lt;/p&gt;
