      <description>
        
        
        &lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;images/How-to-destroy_delete-Microhost-cloud-server-2.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;At first, you need to login &lt;a href=&#34;https://cloud.microhost.com/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Microhost Cloud Dashboard&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Select the cloud server that you want to delete.&lt;/li&gt;
